data.description: This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is ready for you. This home is lacking nothing and rich in character. You will love the spacious driveway providing plenty of parking. There is a great sized, detached single car garage. The living room is large and connects to the kitchen. The kitchen has lots of counter space and storage space. The breakfast nook is a great size. There is a full bathroom off the kitchen perfect for guest use. You will love the size of both bedrooms. The master bedroom is a great size and has a large walk-in closet with lots of shelves and built ins as well as an on suite full bathroom. The backyard is large, and privacy fenced with a brand-new fence. The detached single car garage is spacious and has an automatic garage door on it. This is a MUST SEE.
